snippet.title: Cyclod longplay (Apple II - Sirius)
snippet.description:
Cyclod (https://www.giantbomb.com/cyclod/3030-51029/) was an action game published by Sirius in 1981 for the Apple ][. The player controls an eyeball whose goal is to kill snakes by shoving bricks at them. After completing Level 7, the game will show you a short cartoon between every couple of levels. Hope you enjoy the longplay!

PS: The # of lives is stored at address $7025. To get infinite lives, change $8075 from CE to AD.

Credits:
Cover art - www.giantbomb.com
